               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-1387" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1387" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1387" type="surname" value="GRIGG"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1387" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM GRIGG</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep the Plough, at Lewisham. The prisoner, with two more men, and two women, came to my house in company—they had two pots of beer, and while I was sitting in the bar the prisoner walked out with a pot—I followed him to the top of Blackheath-hill—I there saw</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183906170268"></xptr>
               <p>him throw it away—he walked on fast—I went after him—he abused me, and I went to the station-house—he and the two girls walked on—the po<lb></lb>liceman and I went and took the prisoner—this is my pot.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-1388" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1388" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1388" type="surname" value="MUMFORD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1388" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY MUMFORD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the officer. I went to the place the prose<lb></lb>cutor described, and found the pot—I then went and took the prisoner—he threw himself on the ground, and said he would not go—we had a great struggle.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> While I was calling for the second pot of beer, the men went on, and they had not paid for the beer—I followed them with the pot and beer in my hand—I called to them—they did not stop—I went on till the publican came up with me—I said, "Will you take the pot?"—he said, "No"—I put it down, and went on with the females across the heath—I was not sober.</p>
               <p>
